NHL ENTRY DRAFT
June 23, 2001
Jiri Novotny
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT
 
 
  
 
  
  
   
 
Q.  Can you just comment on your excitement, your feelings, the emotions of being drafted?
 
JIRI NOVOTNY: I am very happy right now and I am very excited.  I am very honored that I have been drafted by Buffalo in the first round.  And it's something fantastic and it's hard to describe it.  
 

Q.  What do you know about the Buffalo Sabers outside of Dominik Hasek?
 
JIRI NOVOTNY: I don't know very much of the city, but I am looking forward to being there because I know that there are some Czech players, so I am going to have some friends, so I am looking forward to being there.   
 

End of FastScripts....

END_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT